These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, raspberry, pumpkin, radish
4 different pets are kept: pony, guinea-pig, bird, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, ship, bike
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person driving the bike is the owner of the pony##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person driving the ship and the person eating raspberry##2
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | pumpkin | radish  | raspberry | lettuce  |
| Pet         | rabbit    | guinea-pig  | pony       | bird     |
| Transport   | ship     | boat | bike       | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, baking, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, satire, epic, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
5. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | gardening | camping    | traveling  | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | spy  | satire   | epic    |
| Sport         | golf | weightlifting | ice-hockey | skiing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, juice, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, hip-hop, reggae, ambient
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of ambient and the person drinking cola##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
6. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola | coffee         | hot-chocolate   | juice    |
| Hobby         | baking | woodworking | reading | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | hip-hop        | ambient      | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, egyptian, japanese, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, baseball, badminton, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, helicopter, van
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the van and the nigerian##2
3. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the spanish##1
6. the person driving the van is between the person who's sport is handball and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | nigerian        | egyptian   | spanish | japanese |
| Sport         | badminton | handball | baseball    | biathlon |
| Transport     | helicopter       | taxi     | van       | subway    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, sprite, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, board-games, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, badminton, water-polo, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person drinking water and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | water | cola      | hot-chocolate       | sprite   |
| Hobby      | baking   | card-games  | traveling | board-games     |
| Sport      | badminton     | sailing | water-polo        | cycling |

