.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, apple, radish, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, card-games, filmmaking, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, climbing, weightlifting, handball
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating apple##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
6. the person eating apple is between the person eating pear and the person eating radish##2
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | radish | apple  | pear | kale      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | singing  | reading | card-games |
| Sport   | handball | rugby | climbing | weightlifting     |

