.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, nectarine, lime, orange
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, adventure, thriller, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, soccer, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person eating nectarine is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
7. the person eating orange is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | lime  | nectarine    | orange | peas  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | action       | adventure        | animation    |
| Sport         | tennis | cricket | rugby  | soccer |

