.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, puzzles, video-games, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, animation, time-travel, horror
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, goldfish, rat
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing  | puzzles | video-games | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | horror | animation   | time-travel         |
| Pet           | pony | goldfish  | frog   | rat      |

