1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating artichoke##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the fan of reggae and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | cranberry  | artichoke    | lime | cauliflower       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | skydiving | reading  | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | soul      | hip-hop  | gospel     |

