The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, sports, documentary, epic
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
3. the person eating tomato is between the person eating zucchini and the person who's hobby is singing##2
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating kale##1
7. the person watching epic movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
