.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, banana, lime, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, magic-tricks, chess, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, snake, cat
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the owner of the snake is the person eating banana##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is chess##2
4. the person who's hobby is chess is between the owner of the horse and the person eating watermelon##2
5. the person who's hobby is chess is the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | watermelon  | lime | pear | banana     |
| Hobby   | singing | chess   | woodworking  | magic-tricks    |
| Pet     | goldfish        | cat       | horse      | snake |

