1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water | fanta     | soy-milk | milk       |
| Hobby      | woodworking  | hiking | cooking  | drawing |
| Pet        | fish  | rabbit      | chinchilla        | hamster      |

