1. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is the videographer##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the journalist##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the tram is between the person watching crime movies and the videographer##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the tram is the paramedic##1

