.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, reading, woodworking, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, pilot, coach, bartender
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, volleyball, tennis, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is the bartender##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the writer and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is volleyball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | woodworking   | reading           | photography         | rock-climbing      |
| Job     | writer | coach | bartender | pilot |
| Sport   | tennis     | volleyball         | water-polo       | skiing        |

