.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, coffee, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, metal, indie, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, malaysian, brazilian, australian
1. the fan of disco is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking coffee and the malaysian##2
3. the person drinking coffee is the fan of metal##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of indie and the australian##2
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the polish is between the brazilian and the fan of dubstep##2
7. the fan of disco is the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | milk | coffee | tea   | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | metal    | indie   | dubstep     |
| Nationality   | australian  | brazilian | polish | malaysian   |

