.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, fanta, milk
There 4 different types of food: peach, grapefruit, lettuce, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skiing, biathlon, cycling
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lettuce is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | almond-milk | milk           | fanta |
| Food       | peach | lettuce    | grapefruit          | nectarine   |
| Sport      | biathlon  | skiing   | cycling | ice-hockey  |

