The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, satire, comedy, family
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, turtle, hamster
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching drama movies##2
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking water##1
6. the owner of the hamster is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the goldfish##2
7. the person watching family movies is the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | lemonade | iced-tea     | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | family        | comedy  | satire  |
| Pet           | goldfish      | hamster         | ferret | turtle |

