.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, writer, entrepreneur, pilot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, parkour, cycling, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, tram, train
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the person driving the trike##1
3. the photographer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the tram is the pilot##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | photographer        | pilot  | entrepreneur | writer   |
| Sport       | badminton | volleyball | cycling    | parkour |
| Transport   | trike        | tram     | train       | motorbike      |

