.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, kiwi, onion, mango
4 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, frog, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, boat, snowmobile, tram
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the tram is the owner of the lizard##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person eating mango and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | mango | kiwi | pineapple | onion |
| Pet         | rat       | guinea-pig     | frog   | lizard   |
| Transport   | bus | boat | snowmobile | tram |

 